msgid ""
"*Imposing Boundary Conditions on Neural Operators via Learned Function "
"Extensions.* Sepehr Mousavi, Siddhartha Mishra, Laura De Lorenzis (2026)."
" `arXiv:2602.04923 <https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.04923>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/mousavi2026.rst:12
#: a7ec1bbc21834da284d0d0ed6cf8db60
msgid ""
"The original code used DOLFINx / FEniCSx; the "
"``examples/solid/mousavi2026/`` directory ports the entire 17-file, "
"18-dataset pipeline onto TensorMesh's PyTorch backend. The payoff is GPU "
"acceleration and end-to-end differentiability — useful both for "
"*generating* the training data and for the neural-operator workflows that"
" consume it."
msgstr ""

